Identifies a super product within an APRA-regulated fund. The USI may be the APRA-regulated fund’s ABN with 3 additional digits, or the fund’s current super product identification number (SPIN).SMSFs don't have a USI – the Australian business number (ABN) acts as the fund identifier.
